---
const faqs = [
  {
    question: "What does your home inspection service cover?",
    answer: "The defects inspection cover issues ranging from tiles, painting, carpentry, workmanship, electrical, plumbing and more."
  },
  {
    question: "How long does a typical inspection take?",
    answer: "A typical inspection takes between 1.5 to 3 hours depending on the size of the property and if the unit is furnished."
  },
  {
    question: "Do I need to be present during the inspection?",
    answer: "It's not necessary for the owner to be present for the initial round of inspection. However, it is encouraged for the owner to be present during the joint inspection with BSC/MA."
  },
  {
    question: "How soon can I expect to receive the inspection report?",
    answer: "You can expect to receive the inspection report within 2 working days after the inspection is completed."
  },
  {
    question: "Will you help us to submit the defects to BSC/MA for rectification?",
    answer: "We will compile and submit the reports to the relevant parties for rectification and you will be notified of the progress."
  },
  {
    question: "What is the 'free renovation consultation' that is provided with your packages?",
    answer: `We know renovation is a tough and mentally tiring process. Therefore for a limited time only, if you book an inspection with us, we include a complimentary 3-month renovation consultation to ease the process and aim to alleviate your headaches.
              <br/><br/>
              In this interactive consultation, we will dedicate a platform between you and our staff to answer your questions and concerns with regards to your renovation, things to look out for and offer possible solutions for your home renovation.`
  },
  {
    question: "When should I schedule a defects inspection?",
    answer: `A defects inspection should typically happen:
              <ul>
                  <li>After HDB key collection for BTOs, when BSC is liable for rectification of defects.</li>
                  <li>After condominium hand over, in which the management should be informed of any defects.</li>
                  <li>After home renovation by IDs/contractors to check for any workmanship issues.</li>
                  <li>Before or after renting to a tenant to check for existing defects or any defects that may be caused by the tenant during their stay.</li>
              </ul>`
  },
];
---
<section id="faq" class="section-padding bg-white">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-primary mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1.5 bg-secondary mx-auto mb-6"></div>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 font-medium leading-relaxed">
        Find quick answers to common questions about our inspection services.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      {faqs.map((faq, index) => (
        <div class="mb-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 bg-light-bg overflow-hidden">
          <input type="checkbox" id={`faq-${index}`} class="hidden peer faq-checkbox" />
          <label 
            for={`faq-${index}`} 
            class="relative flex items-center p-5 cursor-pointer text-lg font-semibold text-primary select-none"
          >
            <div class="relative w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 shrink-0">
              <span class="bar-1 absolute w-5 h-0.5 bg-secondary rounded-full transition-transform duration-300"></span>
              <span class="bar-2 absolute w-5 h-0.5 bg-secondary rounded-full transition-transform duration-300"></span>
            </div>
            {faq.question}
          </label>
          <div class="max-h-0 peer-checked:max-h-screen overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out">
            <div class="p-5 pt-0 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed" set:html={faq.answer} />
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-12">
      <h3 class="text-xl text-gray-600 font-medium leading-relaxed">
        Still have questions? 
        <a href="#contact" class="text-secondary hover:underline font-semibold">Contact us</a> and we'll be happy to help!
      </h3>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .faq-checkbox:checked + label .bar-1 {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }
  .faq-checkbox:checked + label .bar-2 {
    transform: rotate(135deg);
  }
</style>
